00:11:11.390 --> 00:11:13.340 align:middle line:84%
But when we are
precognitive when awake,

00:11:13.340 --> 00:11:16.265 align:middle line:84%
it's always the body
that knows before we do.

00:11:16.265 --> 00:11:17.140 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:11:17.140 --> 00:11:18.710 align:middle line:84%
>>CHEUNG: But in the
dream state, of course,

00:11:18.710 --> 00:11:19.730 align:middle line:90%
the body's asleep.

00:11:19.730 --> 00:11:21.500 align:middle line:90%
We're pure intuition.

00:11:21.500 --> 00:11:23.960 align:middle line:84%
That's why most
precognitions happen.

00:11:23.960 --> 00:11:27.370 align:middle line:84%
I would say about 95
plus precognitions

00:11:27.370 --> 00:11:29.390 align:middle line:84%
happen in the dream
state for that reason,

00:11:29.390 --> 00:11:31.550 align:middle line:84%
because we haven't got
material distractions.

00:11:31.550 --> 00:11:34.832 align:middle line:84%
However, in the waking state,
we get that gut instinct.

00:11:34.832 --> 00:11:36.290 align:middle line:84%
There's a reason
we have that word.

00:11:36.290 --> 00:11:37.130 align:middle line:90%
It's in the body.

00:11:37.130 --> 00:11:39.050 align:middle line:84%
And of course, that's going
to happen at night too.

00:11:39.050 --> 00:11:40.760 align:middle line:84%
So if you can't remember
any of your dreams,

00:11:40.760 --> 00:11:42.380 align:middle line:84%
check in with your
body first thing.

00:11:42.380 --> 00:11:45.320 align:middle line:84%
That's why I said send healing
love to every part of your body.

00:11:45.320 --> 00:11:47.150 align:middle line:84%
See what your gut is
trying to tell you,

00:11:47.150 --> 00:11:49.700 align:middle line:84%
what your heart's trying to
tell you about the day ahead.

00:11:49.700 --> 00:11:53.392 align:middle line:84%
And then write in your
journal how you feel.

