00:14:13.780 --> 00:14:16.110 align:middle line:84%
How you feel about
yourself in the inside out

00:14:16.110 --> 00:14:19.720 align:middle line:84%
is what you tend to attract
in your waking life.

00:14:19.720 --> 00:14:21.570 align:middle line:90%
It matters.

