with a skepticism.

00:42:03.460 --> 00:42:06.900 align:middle line:84%
This was a way to maybe
reach more mainstream.

00:42:06.900 --> 00:42:09.750 align:middle line:84%
People who normally wouldn't
read my nonfiction books.

00:42:09.750 --> 00:42:12.250 align:middle line:84%
